data.description: Flawless Hill Country Views! This 2 story, red brick home sits on slightly over 5 acres. On the second level, it offers 3 bedrooms showcasing panoramic views of the rolling Texas Hill Country, along with 2 conveniently located bathrooms. Downstairs you'll find 2 large living areas, along with a granite countertop-lined kitchen and a breakfast nook; all of which offer spectacular visibility of the valleys and ridges below. Additionally, a half bath is located in the main living area. This homestead provides seclusion from neighbors on all sides, a rainwater collection system, small outdoor shed, and a chicken coop. Even more, a LOW tax rate! New roof and new A/C!       The home is also ideally located directly between Helotes and Bandera. Take advantage of all the amenities the city has to offer, while the highly desired country life lies in your own backyard. Schedule a showing today!
